# Project Architecture Rules

This project follows a feature-based architecture.

src/
  features/
  components/
  hooks/
  services/
  lib/
  types/

Feature structure:

features/<feature>/
  components/
  hooks/
  services/
  types.ts

Separation of concerns:

components → UI
hooks → state + logic
services → Supabase access
types → models
lib → utilities

Components must never call Supabase directly.
All DB calls go through services.